00:00:01.960 --> 00:00:05.930
♫ ♫

00:00:05.930 --> 00:00:09.400
♫ ♫

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:13.440
♫ ♫

00:00:14.359 --> 00:00:16.564
When was it exactly

00:00:16.564 --> 00:00:20.840
that I started being unable
to take my eyes off him?

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:24.640
♫ ♫

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:30.360
♫ ♫

00:00:32.050 --> 00:00:35.420
♫ ♫

